# Payment & Booking Feature

## Feature Overview

This feature allows customers to review booking information, complete payment, and successfully reserve movie tickets.

---

## User Story

As a customer,

I want to review my booking details and complete payment,

So that I can reserve seats and receive confirmation.

---

## Acceptance Criteria

### Booking Summary

The system shall display:

- Movie name
- Showtime
- Selected seats
- Quantity of seats
- Total price

### Payment

The system shall support fake payment (mock payment).

Payment processing time: approximately 2–3 seconds.

### Booking API

The system shall call Booking API after payment succeeds.

Example request:

POST /api/bookings


Payload:

{
    movieId,
    showtimeId,
    seatIds,
    totalAmount
}


### Success Page

After successful booking:

User shall be redirected to Success Page.

Success page contains:

- Booking ID
- Movie name
- Showtime
- Seats
- Total amount
- Success message
